1
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:35,009
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:39,289
[2005]

3
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:39,729
Who would've thought

4
00:01:39,289 --> 00:01:41,600
[Certificate of Honor]

5
00:01:39,759 --> 00:01:41,500
the first place in this essay contest

6
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:43,160
actually went to Xia Xiaolan?

7
00:01:43,710 --> 00:01:44,910
As if she deserves it.

8
00:01:48,430 --> 00:01:49,590
Are you blind?

9
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,190
Stand up!

10
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:13,710
-Good morning, teacher.
-Good morning, teacher.

11
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:14,680
Good morning, students.

12
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,610
Please sit down.

13
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,750
Please take out your math textbooks.

14
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:21,890
Let's begin today's lesson.

15
00:02:21,890 --> 00:02:23,190
Jealousy is a knife—

16
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,890
sometimes it hurts others,

17
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:27,710
and sometimes it hurts the one holding it.

18
00:02:28,180 --> 00:02:31,700
[Episode 18: The One Holding the Knife]

19
00:02:34,079 --> 00:02:34,750
Chen,

20
00:02:35,470 --> 00:02:36,800
the Asian Games is

21
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,120
a huge opportunity for our brand!

22
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,440
Right now, the biggest sporting event

23
00:02:39,230 --> 00:02:41,400
[Luna]

24
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:40,590
our country can host

25
00:02:40,590 --> 00:02:41,520
is the Asian Games.

26
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,860
[The Asian Games Torch Relay Begins Today]

27
00:02:41,810 --> 00:02:43,370
We won't be able to host the Olympics

28
00:02:42,860 --> 00:02:44,210
[Starting from the Himalayas,
Carrying the Light of the Games]

29
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:43,960
until 2008,

30
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,560
you know?

31
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:46,000
Asian Games lottery tickets!

32
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,310
Get your lottery tickets here, everyone!

33
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:47,750
Two tickets.

34
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:49,120
Sir, do you want two?

35
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:50,810
Here, two tickets!

36
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,120
Here, five tickets! Here!

37
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,430
Three tickets!

38
00:02:53,430 --> 00:02:54,400
Let's support the Asian Games!

39
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,960
Three tickets, alright!

40
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:58,050
Sir, I won the second prize!

41
00:02:58,150 --> 00:02:59,280
I won!

42
00:02:59,310 --> 00:02:59,980
[Happy Home]

43
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:00,960
Hello.

44
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,490
Welcome to Happy Home Materials!

45
00:03:02,490 --> 00:03:03,240
Here, take a look.

46
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,280
Right now, for in-store purchases...

47
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:04,910
Hello.

48
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,190
Customers who spend 999 yuan or more today

49
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:07,950
can receive an Asian Games souvenir.

50
00:03:07,950 --> 00:03:09,550
[The Spirit of Asia; The 11th Asian Games]

51
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:17,430
-Go China!
-Go China!

52
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:23,620
♪ The spirit of Asia,
as one we will stand ♪

53
00:03:17,590 --> 00:03:18,960
-Go China!
-Go China!

54
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:20,630
-Go China!
-Go China!

55
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,400
-Go China!
-Go China!

56
00:03:22,590 --> 00:03:24,120
-Go China!
-Go China!

57
00:03:23,890 --> 00:03:31,180
♪ The spirit of Asia,
bring on all the joy ♪

58
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,310
-Go China!
-Go China!

59
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:38,010
♪ The spirit of Asia,
striving the best we can ♪

60
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:45,650
♪ The spirit of Asia,
let's join hand in hand ♪

61
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:52,540
♪ Asia will always be
the pride of all our lives ♪

62
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:52,680
Take your time browsing.

63
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,750
Feel free to try them on.

64
00:03:53,090 --> 00:04:00,130
♪ The pride of all our lives ♪

65
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,710
Would you like to pair it with a bag?

66
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:57,120
How is it? See anything you like?

67
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:57,800
It matches your shoes—

68
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,750
a perfect complement.

69
00:03:58,750 --> 00:03:59,520
Here, try it.

70
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:00,310
You can try it on.

71
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:02,040
The fitting room is over there.

72
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:02,750
Okay.

73
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:07,400
♪ The pride of all our lives ♪

74
00:04:06,630 --> 00:04:07,630
Mr. Chen, your business is really booming!

75
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:08,560
Thank you, thank you.

76
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,890
No problem. No problem.

77
00:04:10,670 --> 00:04:14,310
♪ The pride of all our lives ♪

78
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,620
Is seven o'clock okay?

79
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,840
I'll arrange it. I'll handle it.

80
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:15,470
Don't mention it.

81
00:04:15,470 --> 00:04:16,360
Okay, okay.

82
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,040
This collar here—

83
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:24,480
make it a bit wider.

84
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,310
Make it an off-the-shoulder style.

85
00:04:25,310 --> 00:04:25,800
Okay.

86
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:26,680
It looks better that way.

87
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,240
Chen,

88
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,920
our branch stores are about to open.

89
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:31,320
Why haven't we seen
any movement from Ji Ya?

90
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:32,830
My friend at the Longcheng Garment Factory

91
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:33,600
told me

92
00:04:33,830 --> 00:04:34,720
that Ji Ya has placed
a bulk order with them

93
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,950
for ready-made clothes.

94
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,560
The main production run was already done,

95
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,120
but

96
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:39,920
she wasn't satisfied with the buttons.

97
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,159
They didn't meet her requirements.

98
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:42,090
So Ji Ya has decided

99
00:04:42,090 --> 00:04:42,920
to order a batch of

100
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,480
custom-made buttons overseas.

101
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:46,700
So production is halted,
just waiting for the buttons.

102
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:48,360
That level of perfectionism does sound

103
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,800
very much like

104
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,800
Ms. Ji Ya's style.

105
00:04:53,830 --> 00:04:55,630
From a designer's perspective,

106
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:57,310
I actually envy her.

107
00:04:58,020 --> 00:04:58,950
She has deep enough pockets

108
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:00,210
to pursue perfection.

109
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:01,820
Pursuing perfection is great,

110
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:03,410
but we have to consider
the domestic market,

111
00:05:03,410 --> 00:05:05,210
mass appeal, and popular taste.

112
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:06,430
Spending that much

113
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:07,430
on

114
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:08,760
such a subtle detail...

115
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,950
The customer is ultimately the one
who pays,

116
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:12,950
and I don't think they'll pay for it.

117
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:14,720
But Ji Ya should be ready soon.

118
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,750
From what I've heard,

119
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:17,270
Elegance's first batch of garments

120
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:18,920
should be hitting the market soon.

121
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:19,450
Alright.

122
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:20,690
Let's not panic

123
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,120
and stick to our own pace.

124
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,000
We can start opening

125
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,260
franchise stores now.

126
00:05:24,310 --> 00:05:25,920
How are things going with Wu Kaili?

127
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,650
Don't worry.

128
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,750
I've been maintaining my connections

129
00:05:27,750 --> 00:05:28,810
on Wu Kaili's side.

130
00:05:29,210 --> 00:05:30,000
This time, we're offering

131
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,750
a generous and fair endorsement deal.

132
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:32,950
She has no reason to refuse.

133
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:33,510
Alright.

134
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:35,830
Next, we should think about

135
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,850
which time slots to buy for our ads.

136
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:41,690
The dish is here.

137
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,680
Enjoy your meal.

138
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:46,360
Here's the dish.

139
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:47,480
Thank you!

140
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:48,600
Thanks, San!

141
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:50,240
San,

142
00:05:50,270 --> 00:05:51,190
I think we should just

143
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:52,720
invest in your restaurant.

144
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,560
That would be wonderful.

145
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,630
You're all big bosses,

146
00:05:55,630 --> 00:05:57,560
and I can just ride your coattails!

147
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,870
After I close up tomorrow night,

148
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:02,950
let's hit the boxing gym?

149
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:03,630
Sure.

150
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:04,600
Okay.

151
00:06:04,630 --> 00:06:05,560
Enjoy your food.

152
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,390
Xia.

153
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:11,520
I still know some people
at the TV stations

154
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,110
in Shengcheng and Longcheng.

155
00:06:13,110 --> 00:06:14,310
How about I reach out
to my connections first?

156
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:15,630
Local TV stations

157
00:06:15,630 --> 00:06:16,750
don't have enough reach.

158
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,390
The goal of our advertising campaign

159
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:19,040
is not only to expand

160
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,180
our brand awareness—

161
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:21,330
more importantly,

162
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,930
it's to attract franchisees.

163
00:06:22,930 --> 00:06:24,160
We need to strive to expand Luna

164
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:26,560
across the country as quickly as possible.

165
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:29,320
So you mean Hua TV,
the national broadcaster?

166
00:06:31,790 --> 00:06:34,200
Would they air ads

167
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:37,000
for a new private brand like ours?

168
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:39,510
We're not exactly
a long-established brand.

169
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,600
"Dear viewers,

170
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:42,680
that concludes today's news."

171
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,310
I think that time slot right there

172
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:44,970
is perfect.

173
00:06:51,070 --> 00:06:52,120
This time slot?

174
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:54,560
Well...

175
00:06:54,870 --> 00:06:55,330
Well...

176
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,270
Aren't we getting

177
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:58,010
a little ahead of ourselves here?

178
00:06:58,010 --> 00:06:59,070
Exactly, Xiaolan.

179
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:00,180
My dear sister,

180
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,360
you're really dreaming big.

181
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,510
I don't think we can do that.

182
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:05,770
Xiaolan,

183
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:06,950
do you remember my mom's

184
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:08,750
classmate, Ms. Zhan?

185
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,220
You met her at the English competition.

186
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:10,880
I remember.

187
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,830
She seems to have connections at Hua TV.

188
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:13,830
I'll ask her later

189
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,870
and see if I can get an appointment
with the person in charge.

190
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:17,750
Then we can talk in person
when we get back to Jingcheng.

191
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:19,920
That seems like too much trouble
to put Ms. Zhan through.

192
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,190
But

193
00:07:20,190 --> 00:07:21,870
I'm planning to go back to Jingcheng

194
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:22,930
to see what I can do.

195
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,000
Since we managed to

196
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,430
get performers to wear our brand
at the gala before,

197
00:07:25,430 --> 00:07:26,190
we can definitely

198
00:07:26,190 --> 00:07:27,560
secure the ad slot too.

199
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:29,310
Don't dismiss it just yet.

200
00:07:29,310 --> 00:07:30,640
Let's go back together.

201
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:33,360
It's always good to have another option.

202
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:33,920
Okay.

203
00:07:34,630 --> 00:07:35,310
Oh, Chen,

204
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,830
alongside the TV ads,

205
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,480
we also need to push hard
through print media

206
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,480
to promote our new brand ambassador

207
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,480
simultaneously.

208
00:07:40,510 --> 00:07:41,830
I think we need to find someone

209
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:43,430
dedicated to handling that.

210
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,500
Let's go with You Li, okay?

211
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:46,390
Okay.

212
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,510
I've been

213
00:07:47,510 --> 00:07:48,430
keeping an eye

214
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:49,560
on her lately.

215
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,830
At least from what I've seen so far,

216
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:52,310
she's been doing solid work.

217
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:53,560
So I'd like to give her another chance

218
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,360
to grow.

219
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:55,800
Xiaolan,

220
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:57,990
I trust your judgment of people.

221
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,480
I'm just puzzled—

222
00:07:59,659 --> 00:08:01,120
why was she

223
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,680
warming up to me a while back?

224
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,840
At that time, I think she really

225
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:05,600
did seem interested in me.

226
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,310
Could it be that she was moved

227
00:08:07,310 --> 00:08:08,750
by my irresistible charm?

228
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:10,550
But she pulled back too quickly.

229
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,270
Wei,

230
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:13,630
don't flatter yourself.

231
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:15,890
Can't you accept that maybe she realized

232
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,070
she misjudged you

233
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:18,980
and then suddenly came to her senses?

234
00:08:18,980 --> 00:08:19,360
Xiaolan,

235
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,480
you used a word before

236
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,630
to describe guys like him.

237
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:22,630
What was it again?

238
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:25,430
A narcissistic scumbag.

239
00:08:25,770 --> 00:08:26,800
-Scumbag.
-Scumbag.

240
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,330
I... I...

241
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,800
W-When did I ever act like a scumbag?

242
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,530
You played with You Li's heart.

243
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:32,390
I swear to God!

244
00:08:32,390 --> 00:08:33,510
I didn't do anything!

245
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:34,120
Enough!

246
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,780
Let's drink. Come on, cheers.

247
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:41,080
[Jingcheng]

248
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:42,840
Thank you, Auntie.

249
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,100
Here, have some fruit.

250
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,670
Xiaolan,

251
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:51,030
don't blame me
for asking so many questions.

252
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:53,080
You come straight to me wanting to meet

253
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,600
the head of Hua TV's
advertising department.

254
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,080
I have to ask what it's about

255
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,910
so I know what to say to them, right?

256
00:08:57,910 --> 00:08:58,970
Of course, Auntie.

257
00:08:59,090 --> 00:09:00,890
We just want to get the TV station

258
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:02,750
to advertise our clothing brand.

259
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:03,360
Naturally,

260
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:03,840
we'll pay

261
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,500
the advertising fees in full.

262
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,670
It's just that we want

263
00:09:06,670 --> 00:09:07,600
the slot right after

264
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,730
the news broadcast.

265
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,270
We don't know if there's an opening,

266
00:09:10,270 --> 00:09:11,360
so we want to talk to the person in charge

267
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,080
directly.

268
00:09:13,770 --> 00:09:14,770
Right off the bat,

269
00:09:14,910 --> 00:09:16,000
you're aiming for Hua TV

270
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,390
and even the post-news slot?

271
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,200
Xiaolan, has your business

272
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,390
grown that big?

273
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:24,030
Do you remember Auntie Zhan
from the English competition

274
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,070
back then?

275
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,630
She works at Hua TV.

276
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:28,790
I'll have her ask around.

277
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,200
Okay. Thank you, Auntie.

278
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,130
Don't thank me just yet.

279
00:09:31,130 --> 00:09:33,000
We still need to
give her a heads-up first.

280
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,960
We still don't know

281
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,960
whether she'll be able to help,

282
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,360
right?

283
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,530
It's okay, Mom.

284
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:37,550
Xiaolan has also reached out

285
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:38,420
through the magazine agency.

286
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:39,390
We're working on both fronts.

287
00:09:39,390 --> 00:09:39,920
Alright.

288
00:09:40,150 --> 00:09:41,750
Sorry to trouble you, Auntie.

289
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,870
We're family. No need to be so polite.

290
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,600
Stay for dinner tonight.

291
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,360
I won't hear otherwise.

292
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:47,980
[Shengcheng Commercial Bank]

293
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,770
Comrade Liu Fen,

294
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:53,210
here is your freshly issued passbook.

295
00:09:53,210 --> 00:09:53,510
Okay.

296
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:54,080
Keep it safe.

297
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:54,380
Thank you.

298
00:09:54,380 --> 00:09:56,110
It's a bit chaotic around here.

299
00:09:59,150 --> 00:09:59,630
Fen!

300
00:09:59,810 --> 00:10:00,510
Are you done with your business?

301
00:10:00,510 --> 00:10:01,150
Yeah.

302
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:04,790
This is Chief Ma from the police station.

303
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:05,320
Chief Ma, hello.

304
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,150
Hello, nice to meet you.

305
00:10:06,150 --> 00:10:06,750
Hello, nice to meet you.

306
00:10:06,750 --> 00:10:08,150
Comrade Liu Fen's shop

307
00:10:08,170 --> 00:10:10,100
happens to be in our jurisdiction.

308
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,000
She's a woman on her own,

309
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,390
coming to the bank for business often.

310
00:10:12,390 --> 00:10:14,520
I was worried something might happen,

311
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:15,790
so I came along.

312
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:17,200
Thank you.

313
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,750
I'm usually busy with work

314
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:20,960
and lots of meetings too.

315
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:22,240
Thanks for looking out for her.

316
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:24,100
It's my duty. Serving the people.

317
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:25,670
It's already noon.

318
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,480
Let's grab lunch together.

319
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:27,790
Yeah.

320
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:28,480
-Why not join us?
-Sure.

321
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,870
I'll pass. I still have work
at the station.

322
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:30,870
Come on, just a quick meal.

323
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:32,070
No, really, I'm busy.

324
00:10:32,150 --> 00:10:33,240
Next time. Next time.

325
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,040
Then we'll...

326
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,240
We'll get going.

327
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:35,670
Okay.

328
00:10:35,670 --> 00:10:36,360
Next time, you have to join us, okay?

329
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:36,720
Sure.

330
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:37,120
Okay.

331
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,030
Goodbye.

332
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:38,840
Bye.

333
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,030
Goodbye.

334
00:10:42,030 --> 00:10:42,750
Bye. Bye.

335
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,100
You can tell at a glance

336
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,800
that Chief Ma is a decent man.

337
00:10:58,790 --> 00:10:59,910
Ma is very nice.

338
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:02,720
Once, when I went to deposit money,

339
00:11:03,190 --> 00:11:04,320
a thief targeted me.

340
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:06,480
Chief Ma helped me out.

341
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,150
Since then,

342
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:10,110
he's been looking out for me.

343
00:11:12,550 --> 00:11:14,350
Then we really should thank him.

344
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:15,600
How about this?

345
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,600
When we have time,

346
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:18,000
I'll treat him to dinner.

347
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,250
That... That's not really necessary.

348
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,890
I gave him some specialties

349
00:11:23,270 --> 00:11:24,870
I brought back

350
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,440
from my hometown.

351
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:30,560
Actually, I know how Chief Ma feels

352
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:31,510
about me.

353
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:35,160
I made it clear
I didn't feel the same way.

354
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,790
Ma is quite gracious.

355
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:39,790
He never

356
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:42,120
brought it up again after that.

357
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,320
Looks like I have

358
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,540
quite a few rivals.

359
00:11:49,150 --> 00:11:50,590
It just shows that the woman I like

360
00:11:50,590 --> 00:11:51,850
is truly outstanding.

361
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:55,200
Fen,

362
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:56,670
I know.

363
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,270
You don't

364
00:11:58,630 --> 00:11:59,760
want to rush things.

365
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:01,510
It's okay.

366
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:03,240
I don't mind waiting.

367
00:12:03,510 --> 00:12:04,570
We can take it slow.

368
00:12:13,610 --> 00:12:14,670
You mentioned earlier

369
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:16,790
that you ran into a thief.

370
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,530
Does Xiaolan know about it?

371
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,720
Xiaolan has so much on her plate.

372
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,520
She's so busy.

373
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:22,750
I didn't tell her.

374
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,330
Makes sense.

375
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,100
If you told her,

376
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:28,510
she'd only worry.

377
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,400
You really think of everything.

378
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,410
Xiaolan certainly never imagined it.

379
00:12:35,410 --> 00:12:36,050
Back then,

380
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:37,340
she took her mother out

381
00:12:37,390 --> 00:12:38,590
to run a street stall,

382
00:12:38,750 --> 00:12:40,270
striving and fighting to build

383
00:12:40,270 --> 00:12:42,070
a better life for the two of them,

384
00:12:42,550 --> 00:12:43,390
while her mom handled things

385
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:44,150
so well

386
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:45,900
and grew so much.

387
00:12:46,470 --> 00:12:47,800
It's truly impressive.

388
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:55,390
♪ A cool breeze drifts softly
through my coat ♪

389
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:59,530
♪ Summer slips away without a sound ♪

390
00:13:00,730 --> 00:13:05,280
♪ The days rush by,
stirring waves of emotion ♪

391
00:13:05,590 --> 00:13:11,870
♪ I miss that moment, bright with color ♪

392
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:10,470
Who is this beautiful lady?

393
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:14,510
Auntie?

394
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,510
Xiaolan!

395
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:19,810
♪ A gentle breeze
carries you into my heart ♪

396
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:17,270
My Xiaolan,

397
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:19,120
it's been so long since I last saw you!

398
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,390
Auntie, you're getting
younger and younger.

399
00:13:20,390 --> 00:13:21,240
You haven't changed a bit.

400
00:13:20,550 --> 00:13:24,000
♪ In that instant,
you changed my whole life ♪

401
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,000
Not at all!

402
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:24,130
You're the one who's gotten prettier!

403
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:24,870
Come on, sit.

404
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:25,910
Why have you gotten so thin, child?

405
00:13:25,390 --> 00:13:29,250
♪ All the love I've given
can't be measured ♪

406
00:13:25,910 --> 00:13:26,840
No, I haven't. Sit.

407
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:28,030
Come on, let's sit together.

408
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:28,690
Okay, okay.

409
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:31,150
Let me take a good look at you.

410
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:36,770
♪ And now, I no longer fear
the wind and rain ♪

411
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,840
It's been so long.

412
00:13:33,510 --> 00:13:35,200
Auntie, that perm looks great on you.

413
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:35,670
Really? Does it?

414
00:13:35,670 --> 00:13:36,270
Very nice.

415
00:13:36,390 --> 00:13:38,520
Just trying to keep up with the trends!

416
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:39,270
Look at me—

417
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:40,480
how's my lipstick?

418
00:13:39,700 --> 00:13:44,130
♪ Blow, blow, let the wind blow ♪

419
00:13:40,870 --> 00:13:42,120
It's the most popular shade
in Jingcheng right now.

420
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:42,480
It looks great.

421
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,960
I'll get you one next time.

422
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,120
Okay, thank you, Auntie.

423
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:49,560
♪ Wipe away the glistening tears
in your eyes ♪

424
00:13:45,910 --> 00:13:47,770
Did you come back alone this time?

425
00:13:47,870 --> 00:13:48,440
No.

426
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,130
I came back with Zhou Cheng.

427
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,040
Oh, right.

428
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:51,630
This is a bag of

429
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:52,740
the soup ingredients

430
00:13:52,740 --> 00:13:54,090
that Uncle mentioned you love.

431
00:13:54,090 --> 00:13:55,750
So I brought some back for you.

432
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:57,870
Look at this big bag—so heavy!

433
00:13:57,960 --> 00:14:00,360
It's not heavy
with two people carrying it.

434
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,720
How is Tao recently?

435
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:02,950
Is he adjusting well?

436
00:14:03,270 --> 00:14:05,470
I don't need to worry about his studies.

437
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:06,790
It's just that...

438
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:08,640
I'm hoping to

439
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:09,750
get things settled

440
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:11,410
before he starts high school.

441
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,750
I have an appointment this afternoon

442
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:15,720
with someone from the TV station

443
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:17,380
to discuss an advertisement.

444
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:19,120
If the ad deal works out,

445
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:20,720
along with the Luna franchise fees

446
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,690
and the dividends later,

447
00:14:21,690 --> 00:14:23,120
we should be able to save enough money.

448
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,030
After we save enough,

449
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:25,810
we can buy land and build a house.

450
00:14:25,810 --> 00:14:26,530
By then,

451
00:14:26,550 --> 00:14:28,200
we can transfer
Tao's household registration here.

452
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:28,660
Auntie,

453
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:30,480
just give me a little more time.

454
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,960
I'm not rushing you.

455
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,560
You've already done so well.

456
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:35,840
I know.

457
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:36,910
Auntie,

458
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:39,080
when I was at my lowest,

459
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:39,920
it was you,

460
00:14:40,150 --> 00:14:41,200
Uncle, and Tao

461
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,200
who gave us a home.

462
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:43,440
Now that

463
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:44,910
I have the means,

464
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:46,870
I want to give you a home too.

465
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:47,930
The best home I can.

466
00:14:49,390 --> 00:14:50,200
Silly child.

467
00:14:53,050 --> 00:14:54,180
Hearing you say that

468
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,390
is enough for me.

469
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,550
Alright, alright, Auntie. It's okay.

470
00:14:58,550 --> 00:15:00,360
Our Xiaolan is truly capable!

471
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:09,240
Alright, stop trying to fix it.

472
00:15:09,390 --> 00:15:10,660
Let your dad fix it when he gets back.

473
00:15:10,660 --> 00:15:11,300
It's fine.

474
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:13,290
Here, have some fruit.

475
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:15,170
The cantaloupe is very sweet.

476
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:16,790
Mom.

477
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:18,440
Who did Auntie Zhan introduce

478
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:19,360
to Xiaolan?

479
00:15:19,790 --> 00:15:20,720
Will it work out?

480
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:23,080
She said it's the director

481
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:25,240
of the TV station's
advertising department,

482
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,080
surname Min.

483
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:27,810
He's in charge of this.

484
00:15:29,460 --> 00:15:30,260
Director Min.

485
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:33,770
Is it a man or a woman?

486
00:15:36,670 --> 00:15:37,510
A man.

487
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:40,640
Look at you, that's all you think about.

488
00:15:41,150 --> 00:15:42,550
I'm not trying to nag you,

489
00:15:43,180 --> 00:15:44,750
but from Yunan to Jingcheng

490
00:15:44,780 --> 00:15:46,000
and then to Shengcheng,

491
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:46,790
you've been following Xiaolan

492
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:47,790
like a lost puppy.

493
00:15:48,870 --> 00:15:49,940
Be honest with me.

494
00:15:50,510 --> 00:15:51,320
What exactly are your intentions

495
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,270
toward Xiaolan?

496
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:56,820
I'm asking you.

497
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:57,720
I fixed it!

498
00:15:57,720 --> 00:15:59,120
Turn it down. It's too loud.

499
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:00,320
Isn't it good as new?

500
00:16:00,670 --> 00:16:02,200
I was asking you a question.

501
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,010
Alright.

502
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:04,600
I'm heading out.

503
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:05,200
I still have things to attend to.

504
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,320
Where are you going?

505
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:07,590
To... pick up Xiaolan.

506
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:09,030
Go then.

507
00:16:10,690 --> 00:16:11,670
When will you ever bring Xiaolan home

508
00:16:11,670 --> 00:16:13,710
as my daughter-in-law?

509
00:16:14,630 --> 00:16:15,790
Has Section Chief Zhan

510
00:16:15,790 --> 00:16:16,910
mentioned our station's situation

511
00:16:16,910 --> 00:16:18,000
to you beforehand?

512
00:16:18,390 --> 00:16:19,440
I asked Auntie Zhan

513
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,570
about it in advance.

514
00:16:20,790 --> 00:16:21,870
She said

515
00:16:21,870 --> 00:16:24,030
some of the ad slots
were available for purchase,

516
00:16:24,030 --> 00:16:25,600
so I came to try my luck.

517
00:16:26,720 --> 00:16:27,600
Try your luck?

518
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:31,360
This has nothing to do with luck.

519
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:32,910
I'll be straight with you—

520
00:16:32,910 --> 00:16:34,910
yes, advertising slots can be purchased,

521
00:16:34,910 --> 00:16:36,600
but the content must be reviewed.

522
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:37,150
However,

523
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:39,510
we've never aired a clothing brand before.

524
00:16:39,510 --> 00:16:40,600
And different time slots

525
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:41,930
have different prices.

526
00:16:43,150 --> 00:16:45,390
Which time slot are you looking to buy?

527
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:47,730
Alright.

528
00:16:48,030 --> 00:16:49,030
Since you're being direct,

529
00:16:49,030 --> 00:16:50,480
I won't beat around the bush either.

530
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,240
We want the slot

531
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:52,960
immediately following the news broadcast.

532
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,220
Please give us a quote.

533
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:59,440
The slot after the news?

534
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,670
That time usually features ads

535
00:17:01,670 --> 00:17:02,790
for bicycles,

536
00:17:02,870 --> 00:17:04,400
watches, and electronics.

537
00:17:05,109 --> 00:17:07,109
Do you know how big those brands are?

538
00:17:08,790 --> 00:17:09,790
You name the price,

539
00:17:09,790 --> 00:17:10,680
and I'll pay.

540
00:17:10,790 --> 00:17:11,910
As long as the ad passes review,

541
00:17:11,910 --> 00:17:12,950
we have a deal.

542
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,270
The closer to the news broadcast,

543
00:17:22,270 --> 00:17:23,470
the higher the price.

544
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:26,790
Ms. Xia,

545
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:29,240
which specific slot do you want?

546
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:31,480
The very first one,

547
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:32,680
right after the news.

548
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:38,510
Ms. Xia.

549
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:42,060
Looks like the meeting went well.

550
00:17:42,060 --> 00:17:42,920
When did you get here?

551
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:43,550
Just now.

552
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:44,720
How did it go?

553
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:47,410
Zhou Cheng,

554
00:17:47,910 --> 00:17:48,610
everyone else thinks

555
00:17:48,610 --> 00:17:50,210
wanting that ad slot

556
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:51,240
is a pipe dream.

557
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:53,590
Only you believe I can pull it off.

558
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:55,240
It's not that I think you can pull it off,

559
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:56,900
but I know that no matter what,

560
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,200
you will give it a try.

561
00:17:58,240 --> 00:17:58,880
Instead of talking you out of it,

562
00:17:58,880 --> 00:17:59,720
I might as well think about

563
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,720
how I can help you.

564
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:02,310
But I didn't expect

565
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:04,640
the advertising fee to be this expensive.

566
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:06,740
It costs a million.

567
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:08,790
How much?

568
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:10,400
A million?

569
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:15,110
Then how about

570
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:17,400
we s-s-switch to a different time slot?

571
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:18,350
No way.

572
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:20,190
I've already put it out there.

573
00:18:20,190 --> 00:18:21,630
I'm set on that time slot.

574
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:23,350
It's fine.

575
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:24,960
Let's shoot the ad first

576
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:26,690
and figure out the money later.

577
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:28,750
Ms. Xia, I knew you

578
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:30,320
wouldn't give up easily.

579
00:18:34,650 --> 00:18:36,540
[A page from Chen Xiliang:
Urgent, return immediately.]

580
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:37,500
It's Chen Xiliang.

581
00:18:38,030 --> 00:18:38,880
Something might have happened.

582
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,140
Let's go back quickly.

583
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:40,830
Let's go.

584
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:41,590
Okay.

585
00:18:44,110 --> 00:18:45,240
The venue and crew

586
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:46,160
are ready,

587
00:18:46,270 --> 00:18:47,790
and we're scheduled to
start shooting tomorrow.

588
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:49,070
The director is already at the hotel,

589
00:18:49,070 --> 00:18:49,720
on standby.

590
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:51,240
Then, out of the blue,
Wu Kaili suddenly told me

591
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:52,300
she wasn't coming.

592
00:18:52,360 --> 00:18:53,690
She says she'll pay the penalty.

593
00:18:53,690 --> 00:18:54,550
What use is that penalty

594
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:55,400
if she's not coming?

595
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:57,200
The whole crew is waiting to shoot.

596
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:58,000
Has her side given

597
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,000
any explanation?

598
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:00,790
Her manager won't see me.

599
00:19:00,790 --> 00:19:03,440
They said they'll just follow
the penalty clause.

600
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:05,500
She's probably found a better offer.

601
00:19:05,590 --> 00:19:07,190
T-Then what should we do now?

602
00:19:07,310 --> 00:19:08,370
Find someone else.

603
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:09,830
The TV station wants the final footage

604
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:10,550
by the 26th.

605
00:19:10,590 --> 00:19:11,400
Go and contact

606
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:13,000
every female star you can reach.

607
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:13,920
I'll check with Wu Kaili's side

608
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,180
to see what's going on.

609
00:19:16,310 --> 00:19:17,160
Time is so tight.

610
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:19,160
Where am I supposed to find someone?

611
00:19:31,790 --> 00:19:34,000
There's a brand called "Elegance."

612
00:19:34,180 --> 00:19:35,780
Have you heard of it, Ms. Xia?

613
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:37,920
Elegance?

614
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:40,310
So it was Ji Ya who poached her.

615
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:42,440
There're plenty of singers in Gangdao

616
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:43,590
more famous than Wu Kaili.

617
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:44,250
She did this

618
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,970
purely to get under my skin.

619
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:47,350
Even someone like Wu Kaili

620
00:19:47,350 --> 00:19:48,690
would back out on you like that?

621
00:19:48,690 --> 00:19:49,440
Don't worry, Ms. Xia.

622
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,900
I'll definitely help you.

623
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:52,000
Why don't I ask her out for coffee

624
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:52,750
so we can talk it through?

625
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:53,350
No need.

626
00:19:53,840 --> 00:19:55,330
Even if she came crawling back right now,

627
00:19:55,330 --> 00:19:56,730
I wouldn't use her again.

628
00:19:57,070 --> 00:19:57,590
Mr. Du,

629
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,590
you did me a favor this time.

630
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:01,240
About you telling Xia Dajun

631
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,900
about my shops in Shengcheng—

632
00:20:03,340 --> 00:20:04,470
I'll let that slide.

633
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:05,200
Thanks.

634
00:20:05,550 --> 00:20:06,440
No, I...

635
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:09,590
What?

636
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:11,370
You upset her again?

637
00:20:12,510 --> 00:20:13,160
Xia Dajun

638
00:20:13,360 --> 00:20:14,780
really went to see Xia Xiaolan?

639
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:16,540
Wasn't it you who told him?

640
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:18,600
You sure acted fast on that.

641
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,270
Go check

642
00:20:19,270 --> 00:20:20,590
what Xia Dajun is doing in Shengcheng.

643
00:20:20,590 --> 00:20:22,590
Okay, okay, I'll go check right now.

644
00:20:39,420 --> 00:20:40,710
[Director: Zhang Guangliang;
Starring: Teresa Li]

645
00:20:44,060 --> 00:20:44,740
[Millennium Icon Teresa Li—
China's International Star]

646
00:20:45,310 --> 00:20:46,170
[Chinese Actress Teresa Li Lights Up
the Serrano International Film Festival]

647
00:20:51,830 --> 00:20:52,310
Ms. Xia,

648
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:52,790
aren't we leaving?

649
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:53,920
Wait for me a moment.

650
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:56,110
Andy?

651
00:20:56,510 --> 00:20:58,030
No "Andy" will work—

652
00:20:58,110 --> 00:20:59,520
we're a women's clothing brand!

653
00:20:59,520 --> 00:21:00,350
Keep looking!

654
00:21:00,590 --> 00:21:02,250
Alright, alright, thank you.

655
00:21:06,310 --> 00:21:07,030
Du Zhaohui!

656
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:12,300
I need to borrow your brick phone.

657
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:25,110
Hello?

658
00:21:25,550 --> 00:21:26,160
Xia.

659
00:21:26,510 --> 00:21:27,440
Check

660
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:28,830
the earliest flight from Hushi

661
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:29,960
to Shengcheng tomorrow.

662
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:31,020
Contact Teresa Li.

663
00:21:31,110 --> 00:21:31,880
Teresa Li?

664
00:21:32,790 --> 00:21:34,030
She is pretty,

665
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:35,520
but compared to Wu Kaili,

666
00:21:35,550 --> 00:21:37,080
isn't she much less famous?

667
00:21:37,170 --> 00:21:37,970
Stop arguing.

668
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:38,880
Listen to me on this.

669
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:39,790
In a couple of years, she'll be so famous

670
00:21:39,790 --> 00:21:40,960
you won't be able to afford her.

671
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:41,750
Okay, okay.

672
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:42,400
I got it.

673
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:47,000
Thanks.

674
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:05,770
Another emergency,

675
00:22:05,840 --> 00:22:07,400
so I used a cheat code again—

676
00:22:08,250 --> 00:22:09,590
drawing on Teresa Li's future fame

677
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:10,520
to benefit Luna.

678
00:22:11,290 --> 00:22:12,620
I don't know if this will

679
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:14,510
accelerate the countdown to my departure

680
00:22:14,510 --> 00:22:16,310
and muddle my memories further.

681
00:22:17,810 --> 00:22:19,610
As soon as I save enough money,

682
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:21,900
I must withdraw from Luna's operations.

683
00:22:30,200 --> 00:22:32,200
Good thing you suggested Teresa Li.

684
00:22:32,450 --> 00:22:34,000
I reached out to everyone
I could think of,

685
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,070
but no one agreed.

686
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:39,440
Either they felt
the schedule was too tight,

687
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:41,900
or they worried about complicated approval

688
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,590
at their workplaces.

689
00:22:44,030 --> 00:22:45,160
Some were concerned

690
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:47,030
that a commercial might
reflect badly on them

691
00:22:47,030 --> 00:22:49,310
and invite gossip from their colleagues.

692
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,110
Only she—

693
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:52,750
the moment I brought it up,
she immediately agreed.

694
00:22:52,750 --> 00:22:54,310
With that kind of personality—

695
00:22:54,310 --> 00:22:55,440
bold and ambitious—

696
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:57,830
she'll definitely be famous one day.

697
00:22:57,830 --> 00:22:59,560
Xia, you have an eye for talent.

698
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:02,830
Very good!

699
00:23:06,270 --> 00:23:06,800
Mr. Chen.

700
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:07,880
Ms. Li.

701
00:23:09,830 --> 00:23:10,690
You're Ms. Xia?

702
00:23:13,030 --> 00:23:15,350
I didn't expect you to be
so young and beautiful.

703
00:23:15,350 --> 00:23:17,150
You should film the ad yourself.

704
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:18,900
You flatter me, Ms. Li.

705
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:20,410
Not everyone can act.

706
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,510
My ambition lies elsewhere.

707
00:23:21,510 --> 00:23:22,910
I'll pass on filming ads.

708
00:23:24,200 --> 00:23:25,600
Thank you so much, Ms. Li,

709
00:23:25,720 --> 00:23:27,380
for saving Luna from a crisis.

710
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:30,070
No need to be so formal, Mr. Chen.

711
00:23:30,070 --> 00:23:31,440
When the ad airs on TV,

712
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:33,560
my face will be on it every day.

713
00:23:33,840 --> 00:23:34,760
It's a win-win,

714
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:35,510
right?

715
00:23:36,750 --> 00:23:37,880
Ms. Li, I didn't expect you

716
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:39,000
to be not only beautiful

717
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:39,800
but also loyal

718
00:23:40,110 --> 00:23:41,040
and farsighted.

719
00:23:42,790 --> 00:23:43,350
Teresa,

720
00:23:43,590 --> 00:23:45,250
we're ready for the next shot.

721
00:23:45,550 --> 00:23:46,070
Coming.

722
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,200
I'll go shoot now.

723
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:48,400
I'll walk you over.

724
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:48,920
Okay.

725
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:05,130
She's poached your brand ambassador?

726
00:24:05,310 --> 00:24:06,640
Ji Ya is going to shoot a commercial too?

727
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:08,160
Judging by Director Min's tone,

728
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:09,070
Ji Ya probably doesn't

729
00:24:09,070 --> 00:24:10,600
plan to run TV commercials.

730
00:24:10,960 --> 00:24:12,640
At least not on Hua TV.

731
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:15,030
But if we're talking about spending big,

732
00:24:15,030 --> 00:24:15,960
we might not

733
00:24:15,960 --> 00:24:17,760
have as much capital as she does.

734
00:24:19,350 --> 00:24:20,000
No.

735
00:24:20,570 --> 00:24:21,660
I need to secure

736
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:22,750
that ad slot quickly.

737
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:24,280
I can't let her beat us to it.

738
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:27,400
Don't push yourself so hard.

739
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:29,490
Life moves at its own pace,

740
00:24:29,830 --> 00:24:31,510
and so can your career.

741
00:24:33,680 --> 00:24:34,480
But...

742
00:24:34,830 --> 00:24:36,400
I don't have much time left.

743
00:24:39,050 --> 00:24:40,890
What do you mean?

744
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:46,110
Property prices are rising

745
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:47,270
so much faster

746
00:24:47,270 --> 00:24:48,270
than I can save up.

747
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:50,440
This wretched real estate market.

748
00:24:50,440 --> 00:24:52,480
If I don't save enough to get in the game,

749
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:54,200
I might be shut out completely.

750
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:55,350
Tao is still waiting for me
to build a house,

751
00:24:55,350 --> 00:24:58,270
transfer his household registration to
Jingcheng, and send him to school there.

752
00:24:58,270 --> 00:25:00,030
You can't keep
putting everyone else's burdens

753
00:25:00,030 --> 00:25:01,630
on your own shoulders, okay?

754
00:25:02,070 --> 00:25:02,750
You can't just

755
00:25:02,750 --> 00:25:03,830
arrange everyone's

756
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:05,160
future for them, right?

757
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:07,070
If I leave,

758
00:25:08,030 --> 00:25:09,960
you'll be the one
whose life I have no clue

759
00:25:09,960 --> 00:25:11,030
how to arrange.

760
00:25:23,790 --> 00:25:25,050
Editor-in-Chief Cui,

761
00:25:25,110 --> 00:25:26,200
didn't we agree

762
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,550
that the second half of the month's cover

763
00:25:27,550 --> 00:25:28,680
was reserved for us?

764
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,020
A fashion show?

765
00:25:32,670 --> 00:25:33,150
Yes.

766
00:25:33,590 --> 00:25:35,510
I know. It's just getting a few people

767
00:25:35,510 --> 00:25:36,680
to walk the runway.

768
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:38,110
It's just a gimmick.

769
00:25:38,110 --> 00:25:39,750
But ultimately,
clothing is all about design,

770
00:25:39,750 --> 00:25:41,070
right? We...

771
00:25:43,440 --> 00:25:44,070
Okay.

772
00:25:45,120 --> 00:25:46,640
Alright, alright. Okay.

773
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:47,270
Okay.

774
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:48,400
Okay.

775
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:50,140
I'll wait to hear from you.

776
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:50,900
Okay, okay.

777
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:56,770
You can still laugh?

778
00:25:57,070 --> 00:25:57,750
You have no idea

779
00:25:57,750 --> 00:25:58,510
how snobbish the media is

780
00:25:58,510 --> 00:25:59,480
these days.

781
00:25:59,750 --> 00:26:01,700
The interview we scheduled
has to be postponed.

782
00:26:01,700 --> 00:26:03,160
And the 10 inside pages we secured

783
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:04,040
are being cut down too.

784
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:04,650
And now,

785
00:26:04,680 --> 00:26:05,830
Editor-in-Chief Cui just called again,

786
00:26:05,830 --> 00:26:06,830
and the cover we were promised

787
00:26:06,830 --> 00:26:07,960
is no longer guaranteed.

788
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:08,590
They want to wait and see

789
00:26:08,590 --> 00:26:10,680
how Elegance's Fashion Show turns out.

790
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:11,740
Let them wait then.

791
00:26:12,070 --> 00:26:12,750
By the end of it,

792
00:26:12,750 --> 00:26:14,680
who knows who will be begging whom?

793
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:21,100
You don't think
their fashion show will be good?

794
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:22,440
Who said that?

795
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:24,070
Ji Ya has spent so many years

796
00:26:24,070 --> 00:26:25,160
in the U.S.—

797
00:26:25,310 --> 00:26:27,110
she's seen things we haven't.

798
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:28,960
As long as she doesn't go overboard,

799
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:30,440
the show will definitely be impressive.

800
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:31,700
Then we're in trouble.

801
00:26:31,750 --> 00:26:32,980
Even you said so yourself—

802
00:26:32,980 --> 00:26:35,110
we'd better think of
a backup plan quickly.

803
00:26:35,110 --> 00:26:35,750
Um...

804
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:37,510
if your magazine idea fails,

805
00:26:37,510 --> 00:26:38,550
do you have a backup plan?

806
00:26:38,550 --> 00:26:39,550
Right, the commercial.

807
00:26:39,550 --> 00:26:40,750
What did the TV station say?

808
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:42,030
If they can't air it,
I'll contact the Longcheng

809
00:26:42,030 --> 00:26:43,640
-and Shengcheng TV stations.
- Stop!

810
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:44,640
No matter how much airtime we secure
in Shengcheng,

811
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:46,160
only people in Shengcheng will see it.

812
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:47,550
Luna's goal is

813
00:26:47,550 --> 00:26:49,210
to expand across the country.

814
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,030
Yes, I know that.

815
00:26:52,030 --> 00:26:53,640
But aren't we short on funds?

816
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:55,240
It's gonna cost one million.

817
00:26:56,530 --> 00:26:57,240
I'm starting to regret

818
00:26:57,240 --> 00:26:59,400
having given Lin Meijuan that much money.

819
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:01,070
I should've paid in installments.

820
00:27:01,070 --> 00:27:01,830
That way, I'd have

821
00:27:01,830 --> 00:27:03,030
more cash on hand now.

822
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:04,440
Chen,

823
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,110
most men would

824
00:27:06,110 --> 00:27:07,110
probably regret

825
00:27:07,110 --> 00:27:08,880
giving so much to their ex-wife.

826
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:09,680
But you—

827
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:11,720
you just wish you'd paid in installments.

828
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:12,850
You're a decent guy.

829
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:13,870
A good person.

830
00:27:14,310 --> 00:27:15,510
You deserve someone better.

831
00:27:15,510 --> 00:27:17,970
Flattering me right now
isn't going to help.

832
00:27:18,030 --> 00:27:18,480
Well,

833
00:27:18,540 --> 00:27:19,200
so, right now,

834
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:20,730
how much are we still short?

835
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:22,450
If needed, I'll sell this.

836
00:27:22,450 --> 00:27:24,310
I know it won't be enough, but still...

837
00:27:24,310 --> 00:27:25,550
Chen, rest assured.

838
00:27:25,550 --> 00:27:27,310
The ad will get through just fine.

839
00:27:27,310 --> 00:27:29,880
But given the current situation,

840
00:27:30,030 --> 00:27:32,760
we might need to
release it earlier than planned.

841
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:33,810
What do you mean?

842
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:34,550
Look,

843
00:27:34,750 --> 00:27:36,010
you have to understand

844
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:37,160
Ji Ya has

845
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:38,400
American investors backing her.

846
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:39,600
It's going to be huge.

847
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:41,590
I heard her fashion show

848
00:27:41,830 --> 00:27:43,240
will be held at

849
00:27:43,270 --> 00:27:44,250
Louvre Square.

850
00:27:44,340 --> 00:27:45,590
By then, everyone will flock there,

851
00:27:45,590 --> 00:27:46,590
and who will pay attention to us?

852
00:27:46,590 --> 00:27:47,270
Really?

853
00:27:48,310 --> 00:27:49,270
That's great.

854
00:27:50,160 --> 00:27:50,830
"Great"?

855
00:27:52,790 --> 00:27:53,750
My goddess, Ms. Xia!

856
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:54,510
I cannot follow a single word

857
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:56,000
you're saying today!

858
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:58,070
She may be the one building the stage,

859
00:27:58,070 --> 00:27:58,680
but the one performing on it

860
00:27:58,680 --> 00:27:59,940
doesn't have to be her.

861
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:01,030
What do you mean?

862
00:28:01,030 --> 00:28:01,830
You want to go?

863
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:03,270
But invitations aren't

864
00:28:03,270 --> 00:28:04,200
that easy to get.

865
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:05,530
How will you attend?

866
00:28:05,590 --> 00:28:07,480
Given Ms. Ji Ya's personality,

867
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:08,550
I bet she...

868
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:12,100
Mr. Chen, Ms. Xia,
someone is here to see you.

869
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:14,440
Good day, Mr. Chen, Ms. Xia.

870
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:15,350
I'm from Elegance,

871
00:28:15,350 --> 00:28:16,610
Ms. Ji Ya's assistant.

872
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:18,960
Elegance is holding a fashion show,

873
00:28:19,310 --> 00:28:20,920
and Ms. Ji has sent me
to deliver invitations

874
00:28:20,920 --> 00:28:21,830
to you.

875
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:23,350
Ms. Ji said

876
00:28:23,550 --> 00:28:24,920
she very much wanted to invite

877
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,160
everyone from Luna,

878
00:28:26,510 --> 00:28:28,480
but unfortunately, seats are limited.

879
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:30,350
Aren't you two partners of the company?

880
00:28:30,350 --> 00:28:31,270
Here are

881
00:28:31,270 --> 00:28:32,530
two invitations for you—

882
00:28:32,530 --> 00:28:34,100
the best seats in the house.

883
00:28:35,550 --> 00:28:36,790
Ms. Ji also said

884
00:28:36,790 --> 00:28:37,960
that she sincerely invites

885
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:39,130
her peers in the business from Luna

886
00:28:39,130 --> 00:28:41,440
to come witness what true fashion is.

887
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:44,590
Please thank Ms. Ji for us.

888
00:28:45,060 --> 00:28:45,920
I'll take my leave.

889
00:28:45,920 --> 00:28:46,640
Thank you.

890
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:48,000
This way.

891
00:28:49,550 --> 00:28:51,150
See? We got the invitations.

892
00:28:52,410 --> 00:28:53,550
[Elegance Fashion Show;
Exclusive VIP Access]

893
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:56,640
Xia,

894
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:59,730
did you study fortune-telling
or something?

895
00:29:00,070 --> 00:29:01,240
You called it.

896
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:15,440
Fashion show?

897
00:29:16,030 --> 00:29:17,290
What is a fashion show?

898
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:18,790
No idea.

899
00:29:20,370 --> 00:29:21,550
Never heard of it

900
00:29:21,550 --> 00:29:22,590
before.

901
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:24,790
I heard these tickets

902
00:29:24,810 --> 00:29:26,340
cost several hundred each!

903
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:28,370
That expensive?

904
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:30,000
There are even scalpers reselling them!

905
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:30,920
No way.

906
00:29:31,590 --> 00:29:32,400
Let's go. Let's go.

907
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:33,800
This isn't a place for us.

908
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:34,440
Let's go.

909
00:29:37,510 --> 00:29:39,650
[Fashion Show]

910
00:29:45,110 --> 00:29:45,640
Wang,

911
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:47,480
don't just focus on the pretty girls.

912
00:29:47,480 --> 00:29:48,760
Take some shots of the venue too.

913
00:29:48,760 --> 00:29:49,820
Editor-in-Chief,

914
00:29:50,310 --> 00:29:51,310
I heard designers

915
00:29:51,310 --> 00:29:52,720
from Gangdao, Japan,

916
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:54,200
and even the U.S.

917
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:54,960
are here.

918
00:29:55,830 --> 00:29:57,360
Ji Ya really pulled a crowd.

919
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:59,030
She's been in the U.S. for years,

920
00:29:59,030 --> 00:30:00,680
and with American investors backing her,

921
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:02,240
it's no surprise she has resources.

922
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:03,840
She really has money to burn.

923
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:05,200
In comparison,

924
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:06,720
Chen Xiliang

925
00:30:06,950 --> 00:30:08,030
is so outdated.

926
00:30:08,310 --> 00:30:10,170
So what if he opened stores first?

927
00:30:10,790 --> 00:30:11,960
In the end, he has to watch

928
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:13,310
others steal the spotlight.

929
00:30:13,310 --> 00:30:14,370
Focus on your work.

930
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:16,570
Don't jump to conclusions so quickly.

931
00:30:22,410 --> 00:30:23,130
Remember—

932
00:30:23,250 --> 00:30:25,200
maintain order at the venue at all times.

933
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,200
One ticket per person.

934
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:26,800
By the way,

935
00:30:26,830 --> 00:30:27,440
tell the ushers

936
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:29,030
to check the seat numbers carefully.

937
00:30:29,030 --> 00:30:29,790
At shows abroad,

938
00:30:29,790 --> 00:30:31,070
people often sit wherever they want.

939
00:30:31,070 --> 00:30:32,430
That will offend the VIPs.

940
00:30:32,430 --> 00:30:33,400
Okay, I'll go see to it.

941
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:34,000
Go.

942
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:39,750
So nice.

943
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:40,480
Okay?

944
00:30:44,820 --> 00:30:45,680
The earrings don't work.

945
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:46,280
Wear another pair.

946
00:30:46,280 --> 00:30:47,010
Okay, Ms. Ji.

947
00:30:48,200 --> 00:30:48,600
Ms. Ji,

948
00:30:48,610 --> 00:30:49,670
how do I look today?

949
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:50,550
Excellent.

950
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:51,520
Walk well.

951
00:30:51,580 --> 00:30:52,580
I'll be watching.

952
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,110
Baby, look.

953
00:30:54,270 --> 00:30:55,400
With so many

954
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:57,590
beautiful models here,

955
00:30:58,310 --> 00:30:59,110
but still,

956
00:30:59,110 --> 00:31:00,970
you're the most beautiful woman.

957
00:31:01,070 --> 00:31:01,640
This is not

958
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:02,720
the right time,

959
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:03,440
honey.

960
00:31:03,790 --> 00:31:05,070
You're worried about something?

961
00:31:05,070 --> 00:31:05,640
Listen,

962
00:31:05,880 --> 00:31:06,930
here, everyone

963
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:07,680
is for you

964
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:08,780
and your brand.

965
00:31:08,960 --> 00:31:09,830
And you're the first-ever designer

966
00:31:09,830 --> 00:31:11,680
to hold a show here.

967
00:31:12,030 --> 00:31:14,490
And it's gonna be a success,
I'm telling you.

968
00:31:14,870 --> 00:31:16,670
Thank you for your support.

969
00:31:17,750 --> 00:31:19,480
I love to support your dream

970
00:31:19,500 --> 00:31:20,230
and career.

971
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:21,030
But

972
00:31:21,030 --> 00:31:22,400
if I support

973
00:31:22,430 --> 00:31:23,190
one more show like this,

974
00:31:23,190 --> 00:31:24,650
I think I'm gonna go broke.

975
00:31:25,200 --> 00:31:27,590
Can you say I'm spending too much?

976
00:31:28,310 --> 00:31:30,350
This is a business battle.

977
00:31:30,550 --> 00:31:31,880
I was just joking.

978
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:32,310
Okay,

979
00:31:32,330 --> 00:31:32,900
enough.

980
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:36,830
I'll need to have a look
at today's celebrity.

981
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:38,880
Yes, boss. Let's go.

982
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:46,750
Ms. Ji,

983
00:31:46,790 --> 00:31:47,850
congratulations!

984
00:31:47,990 --> 00:31:49,160
I didn't expect that in Shengcheng,

985
00:31:49,160 --> 00:31:50,440
someone could hold such an impressive

986
00:31:50,440 --> 00:31:51,240
fashion show.

987
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,470
You know how it is—

988
00:31:52,500 --> 00:31:54,680
in Gangdao,
every inch of space costs a fortune.

989
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:55,920
Trying to organize a big event

990
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:57,040
is no easy feat!

991
00:31:57,110 --> 00:31:57,640
Alright.

992
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,310
The run of show is finalized.

993
00:31:59,310 --> 00:32:00,400
Make sure nothing goes wrong later.

994
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:01,920
No problem. Don't worry.

995
00:32:03,150 --> 00:32:03,680
Also,

996
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:04,880
our Kelly

997
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:07,000
will become the brand ambassador, right?

998
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,130
How are you feeling?

999
00:32:08,790 --> 00:32:09,960
I'm more excited now

1000
00:32:09,960 --> 00:32:11,200
than on any stage I've ever been on.

1001
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:11,680
Ji Ya,

1002
00:32:11,700 --> 00:32:13,640
thank you for giving me this opportunity.

1003
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:14,510
No need to thank me.

1004
00:32:14,510 --> 00:32:15,510
You're the best.

1005
00:32:16,030 --> 00:32:17,070
I'll be watching.

1006
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:24,370
Almost all the guests are here.

1007
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,600
They really all came.

1008
00:32:30,250 --> 00:32:31,140
Who is that?

1009
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:37,960
Isn't that Teresa Li?

1010
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:38,960
She is beautiful.

1011
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:39,510
Really?

1012
00:32:39,510 --> 00:32:40,660
It really is Teresa Li.

1013
00:32:40,660 --> 00:32:41,390
It really is!

1014
00:32:41,750 --> 00:32:43,640
She looks even better in person
than in her films!

1015
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:44,480
Teresa Li!

1016
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:48,250
Teresa Li!

1017
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:49,840
Why is Teresa Li here?

1018
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:51,200
People from Luna are here too.

1019
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:52,160
Quick, go take some photos!

1020
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:52,920
Teresa Li!

1021
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:54,880
She's so beautiful!

1022
00:32:54,880 --> 00:32:56,790
Our whole family loves her!

1023
00:32:57,070 --> 00:32:57,990
Teresa Li!

1024
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:03,150
This place is set up pretty well.

1025
00:33:03,310 --> 00:33:04,110
Yeah, not bad.

1026
00:33:05,550 --> 00:33:06,680
Let's go take a look.

1027
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:10,130
Senior!

1028
00:33:10,160 --> 00:33:11,510
It really is Teresa Li!

1029
00:33:11,510 --> 00:33:12,240
Yeah.

1030
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:13,200
You look

1031
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,240
even better in person than in films!

1032
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,570
Teresa, look over here!

1033
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:16,590
Teresa!

1034
00:33:16,590 --> 00:33:18,200
They're calling for Teresa Li?

1035
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,200
Who is Teresa Li?

1036
00:33:19,590 --> 00:33:20,740
She's a film actress.

1037
00:33:20,740 --> 00:33:21,740
An award-winner.

1038
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:23,880
A mainland actress?

1039
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:26,610
It doesn't matter.

1040
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:27,930
Today's star

1041
00:33:28,030 --> 00:33:28,920
is Kaili!

1042
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:31,000
Xia Xiaolan

1043
00:33:31,350 --> 00:33:33,030
gave the tickets to Chen Xiliang

1044
00:33:33,030 --> 00:33:34,230
and another actress.

1045
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:36,710
Then, she got two tickets herself

1046
00:33:36,710 --> 00:33:38,570
and sat on the side stage instead.

1047
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:40,720
What exactly is she trying to do?

1048
00:33:41,270 --> 00:33:42,960
I'll have security
throw them out right now.

1049
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:43,550
No!

1050
00:33:43,930 --> 00:33:44,750
If you kick them out,

1051
00:33:44,750 --> 00:33:47,070
the papers and magazines
will run wild with speculation!

1052
00:33:47,070 --> 00:33:48,200
No matter how successful

1053
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:49,200
our show is today,

1054
00:33:49,440 --> 00:33:50,680
tomorrow's headlines will

1055
00:33:50,680 --> 00:33:51,440
all be about

1056
00:33:51,550 --> 00:33:53,310
why Teresa Li was kicked out.

1057
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,550
Don't worry.

1058
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:57,460
A mainland actress

1059
00:33:57,540 --> 00:33:58,510
can't possibly match the popularity

1060
00:33:58,510 --> 00:33:59,720
of our Kaili.

1061
00:34:00,990 --> 00:34:02,310
But the boss of Luna

1062
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:03,640
actually managed to secure

1063
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:05,030
such good seats?

1064
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:08,080
I gave them the invitations.

1065
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:12,840
Ms. Ji, you really are...

1066
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:13,760
generous.

1067
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:18,360
Kaili,

1068
00:34:18,710 --> 00:34:19,440
do your best.

1069
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:21,070
You're the only superstar

1070
00:34:21,070 --> 00:34:21,960
of this show.

1071
00:34:24,480 --> 00:34:25,840
Ms. Li! Ms. Li!

1072
00:34:27,070 --> 00:34:27,590
Teresa,

1073
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:29,510
your dress is absolutely gorgeous!

1074
00:34:29,510 --> 00:34:30,690
Do you like this brand?

1075
00:34:30,690 --> 00:34:31,500
This dress

1076
00:34:31,530 --> 00:34:33,170
was provided by Luna.

1077
00:34:33,550 --> 00:34:35,150
It's part of
their fall collection this year.

1078
00:34:35,150 --> 00:34:35,760
Luna?

1079
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:37,730
Is the dress not from Elegance?

1080
00:34:38,510 --> 00:34:39,440
It's Luna's.

1081
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:42,440
The commercial I filmed for Luna

1082
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:43,760
will be airing in the next few days.

1083
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:45,280
I hope you all support it.

1084
00:34:46,460 --> 00:34:47,030
-Okay.
-Sure.

1085
00:34:47,030 --> 00:34:47,800
She actually brought up another brand

1086
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:49,130
right here at our event.

1087
00:34:49,550 --> 00:34:51,190
Has nobody taught her any manners,

1088
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:51,840
or did she come here specifically

1089
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:52,760
to sabotage us?

1090
00:34:53,480 --> 00:34:54,150
Teresa,

1091
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:55,800
how much did Luna pay you

1092
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:56,760
for the ad?

1093
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:58,000
Yeah, can you give us

1094
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:58,670
a figure?

1095
00:34:59,630 --> 00:35:00,490
Please tell us.

1096
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:03,840
Normally, ad fees

1097
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:05,320
can't be disclosed.

1098
00:35:05,520 --> 00:35:06,400
The reporters are probably just

1099
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:07,360
teasing anyway.

1100
00:35:07,650 --> 00:35:08,460
Then...

1101
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:09,930
I won't answer that.

1102
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:11,480
No,

1103
00:35:11,840 --> 00:35:12,770
you must answer.

1104
00:35:13,230 --> 00:35:14,190
Just use the standard response

1105
00:35:14,190 --> 00:35:15,230
I gave you.

1106
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:17,460
Is it inconvenient to tell us?

1107
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:21,320
To be honest,

1108
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:24,090
I've never seen
that much money in my life.

1109
00:35:24,180 --> 00:35:25,140
Luna paid me

1110
00:35:25,510 --> 00:35:26,760
a full 10,000 yuan.

1111
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:29,030
-Ten thousand?
-Ten thousand yuan?

1112
00:35:29,030 --> 00:35:31,430
Seeing that much money actually scared me.

1113
00:35:31,440 --> 00:35:32,470
Just thinking about

1114
00:35:32,470 --> 00:35:33,920
shooting a commercial for a few days

1115
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:35,360
and making that much money—

1116
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:37,280
I couldn't sleep at night.

1117
00:35:38,480 --> 00:35:39,800
Isn't that just capitalism?

1118
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:40,510
Exactly!

1119
00:35:40,510 --> 00:35:41,400
What do ordinary people like us

1120
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,000
earn in a month?

1121
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:43,150
Just a few dozen yuan.

1122
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:44,480
She gets 10,000 just like that!

1123
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:45,880
How much do I make in a month?

1124
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:47,360
Why should you make 10,000?

1125
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:49,840
-Yeah, exactly.
-Yeah.

1126
00:35:50,550 --> 00:35:52,150
That's totally capitalism.

1127
00:35:52,190 --> 00:35:53,190
Luna actually hired

1128
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:54,510
such a stupid actress.

1129
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,550
How could she reveal her pay publicly?

1130
00:35:56,550 --> 00:35:57,760
I told you—

1131
00:35:57,930 --> 00:35:59,190
she's just a small-time actress.

1132
00:35:59,190 --> 00:36:00,590
Nothing to worry about.

1133
00:36:02,230 --> 00:36:03,360
Why do you get to make 10,000?

1134
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:05,190
Serves you right that you can't sleep!

1135
00:36:05,190 --> 00:36:07,200
Our country is still developing.

1136
00:36:07,520 --> 00:36:08,450
Many people

1137
00:36:08,480 --> 00:36:09,880
have only just managed to afford food.

1138
00:36:09,880 --> 00:36:11,280
You wear such nice clothes

1139
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:12,540
and makeup for shoots,

1140
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:13,510
whereas farmers

1141
00:36:13,510 --> 00:36:14,480
toil in tattered clothing

1142
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:15,440
all year,

1143
00:36:15,950 --> 00:36:17,190
yet their whole family's income

1144
00:36:17,190 --> 00:36:18,550
doesn't even come close to a fraction

1145
00:36:18,550 --> 00:36:19,550
of what you earn from one ad!

1146
00:36:19,550 --> 00:36:19,960
-Exactly.
-Yeah.

1147
00:36:19,960 --> 00:36:20,670
Teresa Li,

1148
00:36:20,670 --> 00:36:22,110
do you really think this is appropriate?

1149
00:36:22,110 --> 00:36:23,400
You made your pay

1150
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:24,110
public.

1151
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:25,800
If all other actors follow suit,

1152
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:27,630
t-the impact would be terrible!

1153
00:36:27,630 --> 00:36:28,280
Everyone,

1154
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:30,440
I'll go back and write

1155
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:31,760
a scathing exposé today!

1156
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:33,280
I never hide my identity.

1157
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:34,880
I am Liu Xuan, a reporter from

1158
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:35,520
Jingcheng Evening News!

1159
00:36:35,520 --> 00:36:36,080
Yes!

1160
00:36:44,980 --> 00:36:46,260
No, I...

1161
00:36:46,960 --> 00:36:48,400
What a shot!

1162
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:49,550
I'm using this one!

1163
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:50,760
Yes, yes!

1164
00:36:51,030 --> 00:36:51,800
Alright, that's enough!

1165
00:36:51,800 --> 00:36:52,960
That's enough photos!

1166
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:54,400
You're all ganging up on her

1167
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:55,150
without knowing the full story!

1168
00:36:55,150 --> 00:36:57,110
How could you just
bully a woman like that?

1169
00:36:57,110 --> 00:36:58,550
If you have any questions,

1170
00:36:58,550 --> 00:36:59,950
ask me. I'll answer them.

1171
00:37:00,040 --> 00:37:01,560
-Who are you?
-Who are you?

1172
00:37:02,500 --> 00:37:04,500
I'm Chen Xiliang, the owner of Luna.

1173
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:06,190
I'm the one who paid

1174
00:37:06,190 --> 00:37:07,790
Teresa Li's commercial fee.

1175
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,230
Teresa Li is

1176
00:37:09,230 --> 00:37:10,400
an excellent actress.

1177
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:12,110
She's starred in so many great works,

1178
00:37:12,110 --> 00:37:13,840
and yet I only paid her 10,000 yuan.

1179
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:15,400
"Only 10,000"?

1180
00:37:15,570 --> 00:37:16,810
Do you know

1181
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:18,460
those female stars from Gangdao

1182
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:20,500
demand 100,000 upfront?

1183
00:37:20,840 --> 00:37:21,960
-A hundred thousand?
-A hundred thousand?

1184
00:37:21,960 --> 00:37:22,960
Well... Oh my god.

1185
00:37:22,960 --> 00:37:24,760
So, of course, I chose Teresa Li.

1186
00:37:25,030 --> 00:37:25,670
Besides,

1187
00:37:26,070 --> 00:37:27,440
after I paid her,

1188
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:28,150
she told me

1189
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:29,630
she couldn't even sleep at night

1190
00:37:29,630 --> 00:37:30,890
receiving that money.

1191
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:32,630
She asked

1192
00:37:32,850 --> 00:37:33,590
if she could use

1193
00:37:33,590 --> 00:37:34,920
her 10,000 yuan fee

1194
00:37:35,110 --> 00:37:37,550
to have us make a batch of
school uniforms.

1195
00:37:38,670 --> 00:37:41,070
She said she would personally

1196
00:37:41,110 --> 00:37:42,570
deliver them to children

1197
00:37:42,670 --> 00:37:43,670
in rural schools.

1198
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,230
-She donated it?

1199
00:37:45,230 --> 00:37:46,070
-She donated it?
-She really donated it?

1200
00:37:46,070 --> 00:37:46,670
So,

1201
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,130
I feel very ashamed.

1202
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:49,550
Teresa Li was willing to

1203
00:37:49,550 --> 00:37:51,070
donate her entire acting fee

1204
00:37:51,070 --> 00:37:53,120
to children in rural elementary schools.

1205
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:54,560
As the owner of Luna,

1206
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,230
I'm not that noble.

1207
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:58,340
I don't have her generous spirit.

1208
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:00,110
As for Luna,

1209
00:38:00,130 --> 00:38:00,860
although

1210
00:38:01,680 --> 00:38:02,510
we're still a small,

1211
00:38:02,510 --> 00:38:03,510
new brand

1212
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,960
relying on modest profits
and quick turnover,

1213
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:07,560
today I am making a decision:

1214
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:08,460
from now on,

1215
00:38:08,550 --> 00:38:10,510
for every piece of clothing we sell,

1216
00:38:10,510 --> 00:38:12,000
we'll donate one yuan

1217
00:38:12,430 --> 00:38:14,760
-to children in rural schools.
-One yuan.

1218
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:15,710
Really?

1219
00:38:16,070 --> 00:38:17,130
Well, listen to me.

1220
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:19,110
Since you're all here today,

1221
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:21,110
I'd like to ask all of you here
to be my witnesses.

1222
00:38:21,110 --> 00:38:21,590
From now on,

1223
00:38:21,590 --> 00:38:23,150
we also welcome you

1224
00:38:23,340 --> 00:38:24,440
to help supervise us

1225
00:38:24,440 --> 00:38:26,640
and keep this good deed going together.

1226
00:38:28,590 --> 00:38:29,520
Is that for real?

1227
00:38:29,720 --> 00:38:31,630
You said
that for every piece of clothing sold,

1228
00:38:31,630 --> 00:38:32,570
you'd donate one yuan—

1229
00:38:32,570 --> 00:38:33,650
do you mean it?

1230
00:38:34,070 --> 00:38:35,730
Since I've said it here today,

1231
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:37,150
with all of you reporters present,

1232
00:38:37,150 --> 00:38:38,360
I absolutely will not break my word.

1233
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,480
I mean what I say.

1234
00:38:40,710 --> 00:38:42,040
First, grab attention;

1235
00:38:42,480 --> 00:38:44,320
then provoke misunderstanding
and criticism;

1236
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:45,840
finally, have an unexpected turn

1237
00:38:45,840 --> 00:38:47,040
and reveal the truth.

1238
00:38:48,670 --> 00:38:49,550
Even TVB's high-society drama writers

1239
00:38:49,550 --> 00:38:50,460
couldn't have pulled off

1240
00:38:50,460 --> 00:38:51,720
something this slick!

1241
00:38:52,110 --> 00:38:52,840
If I had known earlier,

1242
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:54,550
I should've asked her to leave just now!

1243
00:38:54,550 --> 00:38:55,400
Didn't you say

1244
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:58,530
that would only make the media
pay more attention to her?

1245
00:38:58,800 --> 00:38:59,480
Afterward,

1246
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:00,960
we could always manage the press

1247
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:03,820
and make sure
they don't write anything out of line.

1248
00:39:06,360 --> 00:39:07,000
Kaili,

1249
00:39:07,150 --> 00:39:08,190
don't worry.

1250
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:10,620
The stage will still be yours in a moment.

1251
00:39:12,230 --> 00:39:13,230
Truly shameless.

1252
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:14,450
Just too shameless!

1253
00:39:14,670 --> 00:39:16,600
Who came up with such a dirty trick?

1254
00:39:17,670 --> 00:39:18,280
Alright,

1255
00:39:18,670 --> 00:39:19,480
don't worry.

1256
00:39:20,510 --> 00:39:21,360
Today

1257
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:22,760
is Elegance's

1258
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:24,090
most important moment.

1259
00:39:24,160 --> 00:39:25,360
We just need to remember

1260
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:25,920
to walk out there

1261
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:27,230
and show our own style.

1262
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:28,750
Tell the host

1263
00:39:28,960 --> 00:39:30,360
to turn the music up a bit.

1264
00:39:30,670 --> 00:39:31,280
Okay.

1265
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:40,480
We're doing an interview here!

1266
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:42,000
Can you turn the music down?

1267
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:42,590
Yeah!

1268
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:43,600
Tell you what.

1269
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:45,330
Here are my business cards.

1270
00:39:45,390 --> 00:39:46,540
Because in a moment,

1271
00:39:46,590 --> 00:39:47,480
the show is about to start.

1272
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:47,960
Okay?

1273
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,290
Let's not disturb

1274
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:49,980
their show.

1275
00:39:50,070 --> 00:39:51,710
-Here, give me one!
-I want one!

1276
00:39:51,710 --> 00:39:53,550
-Me too!
-Me too!

1277
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:55,110
Call me!

1278
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:57,320
I'll answer all of your questions.

1279
00:39:57,320 --> 00:39:57,880
Here.

1280
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:29,560
Ladies and gentlemen,

1281
00:41:29,560 --> 00:41:31,110
please give a warm round of applause

1282
00:41:31,110 --> 00:41:32,550
to welcome once again

1283
00:41:32,570 --> 00:41:34,130
Ms. Ji Ya

1284
00:41:34,680 --> 00:41:36,120
and the famous singer,

1285
00:41:36,150 --> 00:41:37,840
Ms. Wu Kaili!

1286
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:40,280
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

1287
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:42,670
Hello everyone, I'm Ji Ya.

1288
00:41:43,280 --> 00:41:44,630
Thank you all so much

1289
00:41:44,630 --> 00:41:45,670
for coming today.

1290
00:41:46,190 --> 00:41:46,760
Here,

1291
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:48,280
I'd also like to officially announce

1292
00:41:48,280 --> 00:41:49,630
the launch of our brand,

1293
00:41:49,630 --> 00:41:51,030
Elegance!

1294
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,510
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

1295
00:41:58,600 --> 00:41:59,680
Next,

1296
00:41:59,710 --> 00:42:01,320
our brand

1297
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:02,800
will be working more closely

1298
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:04,760
with Ms. Wu.

1299
00:42:04,840 --> 00:42:05,570
For example,

1300
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:07,630
Ms. Wu will shoot

1301
00:42:07,630 --> 00:42:08,960
many commercials for us

1302
00:42:08,990 --> 00:42:09,520
and

1303
00:42:09,550 --> 00:42:10,550
will serve as

1304
00:42:10,550 --> 00:42:13,480
the official brand ambassador!

1305
00:42:15,030 --> 00:42:16,230
-Great!
-Yeah.

1306
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:19,000
Ms. Wu Kaili, may I ask,

1307
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,760
what is your endorsement fee

1308
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:23,110
for representing Elegance?

1309
00:42:23,590 --> 00:42:24,550
-Yeah!
-Please tell us!

1310
00:42:24,550 --> 00:42:25,960
We'd like to know, too!

1311
00:42:26,150 --> 00:42:27,050
That company paid 10,000.

1312
00:42:27,050 --> 00:42:28,670
Did they pay you 100,000?

1313
00:42:28,670 --> 00:42:29,800
-Please tell us.
-Please.
